body:
Also, seems like the `.proto` files don't match up.

In filetree but not script:
`cloud/kernels`
`gdr`
`lite/toco`
`mpi`
`mpi_collectives`
`verbs`

Not sure, if the wildcards match sub-directories as well.
If they don't, the paths have to be expanded respectively.
Needing some clarification by @mrry .

So `tensorboard` should be expanded to:
`tensorboard/graph_explorer/proto`
`tensorboard/plugins/projector`
`tensorboard/plugins/trace`

And `training` should be expanded to:
`training/python/training`
